Patrick Dolezal has given his Buy rating due to a combination of factors related to Rocket Pharmaceuticals’ advancing pipeline and upcoming catalysts. He highlights that the resubmitted BLA for KRESLADI in severe LAD-I now has a March 28, 2026 PDUFA date, and he views the probability of approval as high, supported by a 100% survival rate at 12 months in treated patients versus historically high early mortality.
